%9B%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD-065455937.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAADM8q5TeCvwSKhZaL1Quys19ix_qrdyG786NspGkoEajaFP4G5snpv75OV5zZqnA-PZogeuT4KeCY_ICsoHoM8e0X88BX53eiwgkYRpzh7wQWHnW74m2R6paBCfm02sqwckNzALHkz83TAPJ7CA5Ae3YdcC5k9h7ldgkfXguNYtV</a><br />\n<br />\n...噚晚女廚神、KOL兼主持TVB  節目「媽媽唔易&quot;造&quot;」嘅「「玻璃朱」朱庭萱（Bonnie）喺網上嘅言論亦同樣惹嚟熱議。朱庭萱喺Facebook回應網民留言話：「其實點解睇嘢唔可以睇番轉頭？可能人哋元朗居民唔抵得班黃絲蝦蝦霸霸，自組民團去反抗佢哋呢？警察調兵去清場睇住遊行、你哋又圍人哋警總、又鬧人哋黑警、狗...轉頭打比警察求救、又投訴人哋唔聽電話...你哋自己有無覺得有問題同好矛盾架？當然，打人真係唔啱啦，但永遠一隻手掌拍唔響。某部分市民對黃絲已經忍無可忍、才會用咁激進嘅方法唧...正等於你哋都係用同一藉口話對政府忍無可忍先要咁激進去爭取一樣囉。點都好希望所有人都可以冷靜的。」...<br />\n<br />\n發爛渣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmg94FZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvmg94FZ.jpg&h=0957b1d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuiDX02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuiDX02.jpg&h=db6ea992&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n及後嘗試補救：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnjPkeD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnjPkeD.png&h=070af840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過飲食男女隨即宣布割蓆，不再續約：<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaT1bmJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaT1bmJ.png&h=2bd92919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 新西蘭廚電品牌Fisher &amp; Paykel也宣布即時終止合作：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqykrVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqykrVp.jpg&h=b6bc2956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可見今時今日，元朗暴徒事件後撐警會令你變成過街老鼠！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喜見文宣工作不是徒勞無功，果然終有一日警察同撐警人士廣泛被香港人認識為煽動及支持暴力者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個